---
title: Honey-Glazed Beef & Avocado Salad with Pickled Cucumber & Slivered Almonds
description: Who said a salad can’t be satiating and hearty? Picture this: honey-glazed beef strips, creamy avocado, crisp apple and pickled cucumber, all tossed together in a bowl with fresh cos lettuce. We’re even sprinkling over some crunchy almonds for that all-important texture. Go on, grab a fork and dive in!

*We’ve replaced the radish in this recipe with cucumber due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
